SEED WHEN YOU ARE DONE!

Placebo - The Hut Recordings
8 Disc (Imported) Box Set

Put together to coincide with the  release of Placebo's Battle For The   Sun
album, the Placebo Box Set is essentially the complete Placebo collection. A
must  for every  Placebo fan,  it is  a limited  edition ten  disc box  set,
containing each of the  band's studio albums, a  disc of B-sides, a  further
disc of B-sides and live performances.
